abstract: Gyozo Kulcsar, Hungary's outstanding 29-year-old Olympic gold medalist, displayed a tremendous amount of resourcefulness and determination last night to capture the Martini  Rossi epee honors for the second time.

abstract: Witold Woyda, the bouncy stylist from Poland, topped a strong international field to capture foil honors yesterday as the three-day Martini  Rossi fencing tournament started at the New York Athletic Club.
